00:35:01.920 --> 00:35:08.950
say, "Will you let me

00:35:08.950 --> 00:35:08.960
in?"Thank

00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:10.270
you,

00:35:10.280 --> 00:35:17.310
Father. Thank you, Lord. Will you come

00:35:17.320 --> 00:35:20.510
in, Lord? I thank

00:35:20.520 --> 00:35:23.870
you,

00:35:23.880 --> 00:35:26.109
Lord,

00:35:30.349 --> 00:35:30.359
for

00:35:35.359 --> 00:35:39.510
the door is opening unto us. A new way of

00:35:39.520 --> 00:35:42.390
thinking, a new way of doing things, a

00:35:42.400 --> 00:35:46.190
new way of coming up higher with the

00:35:46.200 --> 00:35:50.710
fire. Glory to God. We worship You,

00:35:50.710 --> 00:35:50.720
O

00:35:50.720 --> 00:35:54.790
Holy One. We worship You, for the Lord is

00:35:54.800 --> 00:35:58.550
good and His mercy endures forever.

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:54.510
First the

00:37:54.520 --> 00:37:58.109
blade, then the ear, then the full

00:37:58.119 --> 00:38:15.480
manifestation of the glory

00:38:16.800 --> 00:38:20.790
upon the land today.

00:38:20.800 --> 00:38:23.510
There will be a great glory flow.

00:38:26.400 --> 00:38:28.829
It will come to the

00:38:28.839 --> 00:38:32.310
ankles, to the knees, to

00:38:32.310 --> 00:38:32.320
the waist-deep,

00:38:32.320 --> 00:38:34.870
and it will go all the way over

00:38:34.880 --> 00:38:37.349
your head. For the glory of the Lord

00:38:37.359 --> 00:38:40.109
