00:38:40.119 --> 00:38:45.550
I

00:38:45.560 --> 00:38:49.630
see it

00:38:49.640 --> 00:38:52.390
like water coming in

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:55.109
like a flow that's deeper.

00:38:57.119 --> 00:38:59.750
As it comes like a mighty wave, a

00:38:59.760 --> 00:39:02.390
mighty rushing wind, it will

00:39:02.400 --> 00:39:04.390
go up higher and higher like the

00:39:04.400 --> 00:39:11.550
tide.

00:39:15.200 --> 00:39:17.589
As you seek Him, you'll find Him. As you

00:39:17.599 --> 00:39:19.829
knock, the door will be open unto you.

00:39:19.839 --> 00:39:22.950
For the castle is Me, and if

00:39:22.960 --> 00:39:25.990
you knock, I will open the door unto you.

00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:59.190
You seek Me and you will find Me.

