00:49:04.160 --> 00:49:07.750
crust. I see contractions; remember

00:49:07.750 --> 00:49:07.760
these

00:49:07.760 --> 00:49:09.990
contractions.

00:49:17.510 --> 00:49:17.520
Look,

00:49:35.760 --> 00:49:47.470
I see Alaska.

