The very thing they are trying to

00:51:10.920 --> 00:51:23.549
manipulate

00:51:23.559 --> 00:51:26.630
will be

00:51:26.640 --> 00:51:33.069
their

00:51:33.079 --> 00:51:36.309
demise. You'll see an uprising in China, in Asia, and

