Queensland. Little fires

00:52:37.920 --> 00:52:44.230
in Queensland,

00:52:49.920 --> 00:52:52.630
Australia.

00:53:06.960 --> 00:53:09.190
China's

00:53:09.200 --> 00:53:12.109
getting

00:53:12.119 --> 00:53:27.470
desperate out of pride. There is

