00:59:40.960 --> 00:59:43.750
to repentance.

00:59:45.760 --> 00:59:48.150
His heart is the harvest, and

00:59:48.150 --> 00:59:48.160
in

00:59:48.160 --> 00:59:50.150
the

00:59:50.160 --> 00:59:51.990
Catholic Church, His heart is the

00:59:52.000 --> 00:59:54.470
harvest. The young

